  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Only on Android: when app syncs there should be blue line in Chats and inside individual chat (e.g. Console). Now, there is no line shown, only text, note that on iOS line is shown.\r\n![screenshot_20171018-210721](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6584810/31737876-2b3af39c-b449-11e7-8841-4539e340306d.png)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nline is shown in Chats and in individual 1-1 chat\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nno line\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- switch to network where app will start syncing (e.g. Ropsten)\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Open Chats -> check for blue line\r\n- Open Console chat -> check for blue line\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: develop\r\n* Operating System: \r\nReal device Google Pixel XL, Android 8.0\r\nReal device Samsung Galaxy S6, android 6.0.1",
